### 1. Create Resource
POST {{baseUrl}}/rbac/createResource
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "profile",
  "slug": "profile",
  "description": "User profile resource"
}

### 2. Create Another Resource
POST {{baseUrl}}/rbac/createResource
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "balance",
  "slug": "balance",
  "description": "User balance resource"
}

### 3. Create Role
POST {{baseUrl}}/rbac/createRole
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "admin",
  "slug": "admin",
  "description": "Administrator role",
  "grants": [
    {
      "resource": "profile",
      "actions": ["create", "read", "update", "delete"],
      "attributes": ["*"]
    },
    {
      "resource": "balance",
      "actions": ["read", "update"],
      "attributes": ["*"]
    }
  ]
}

### 4. Create Another Role
POST {{baseUrl}}/rbac/createRole
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "shop",
  "slug": "shop",
  "description": "Shop owner role",
  "grants": [
    {
      "resource": "profile",
      "actions": ["read", "update"],
      "attributes": ["*"]
    }
  ]
}

### 5. Get List of Resources (No Pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/rbac/listResources
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. Get List of Resources with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/rbac/listResources?limit=10&offset=0
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. Get List of Resources with Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/rbac/listResources?limit=10&offset=0&search=profile
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. Get List of Roles (No Pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/rbac/listRoles
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. Get List of Roles with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/rbac/listRoles?limit=10&offset=0
Content-Type: application/json

### 10. Get List of Roles with Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/rbac/listRoles?limit=10&offset=0&search=admin
Content-Type: application/json

### Test Cases for Validation

### Test: Create Duplicate Resource (Should Fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/rbac/createResource
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "profile",
  "slug": "profile_duplicate",
  "description": "Duplicate resource"
}

### Test: Create Duplicate Role (Should Fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/rbac/createRole
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "admin",
  "slug": "admin_duplicate",
  "description": "Duplicate role",
  "grants": []
}

### Test: Create Resource with Empty Name (Should Fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/rbac/createResource
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "slug": "empty_resource",
  "description": "Test empty name"
}

### Test: Search Non-existent Resource
GET {{baseUrl}}/rbac/listResources?search=nonexistent
Content-Type: application/json

### Test: Search Non-existent Role
GET {{baseUrl}}/rbac/listRoles?search=nonexistent
Content-Type: application/json
